20won%2C%20or%20about%20%2422%20to%20%2437%2C%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMingwan%20Jeong%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Snapshoot%2C%20told%20BI%20his%20business%20serves%20hundreds%20of%20customers%20monthly%20and%20is%20increasingly%20attracting%20customers%20from%20outside%20South%20Korea%2C%20such%20as%20Japan%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20Indonesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Samsung%20released%20the%20S22%20Ultra%2C%20their%20promotional%20slogan%20emphasized%20its%20capability%20to%20'photograph%20the%20moon%2C'%26quot%3B%20Jeong%20said.%20%26quot%3BFans%20quickly%20recognized%20that%20this%20advanced%20camera%20could%20help%20them%20capture%20their%20idols%20clearly%20at%20concerts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Snapshoot%20started%20in%202022%20with%20a%20small%20inventory%20of%2010%20phones%2C%20but%20now%20keeps%20several%20hundred%20smartphones%20in%20stock%20at%20any%20given%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20example%20is%20Woori%20Mobile%20Service%2C%20a%20South%20Korean%20telecommunications%20company%C2%A0that%20started%20renting%20out%20phones%20in%202023.%C2%A0Its%20collection%20points%20are%C2%A0at%20Seoul's%20Konkuk%20University%20and%20the%20hip%20Sinchon%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eneighborhood.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20pickup%20point%20at%20Seoul's%20Incheon%20airport%2C%20catering%20to%20Woori's%20foreign%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20them%20didn't%20own%20the%20latest%20smartphones%20or%20didn't%20want%20the%20hassle%20of%20international%20roaming%2C%26quot%3B%20Han%20Da%20Bean%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Woori%20Mobile%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20offers%20rentals%20of%20the%20S23%20and%20S24%20models%2C%20charging%2035%2C000%20won%20or%20about%20%2425%20per%20day%2C%20and%20a%2010%2C000%20won%20daily%20reservation%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woori%20Mobile%2C%20a%20South%20Korean%20telecommunications%20company%2C%20offers%20day%20rentals%20of%20Samsung%20phones%2C%20which%20come%20in%20handy%20pouches.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68258477c6ad288d1480fd70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWoori%20Mobile%20Service%2C%20a%20South%20Korean%20telecommunications%20company%2C%20offers%20day%20rentals%20of%20Samsung%20phones%2C%20which%20come%20in%20handy%20pouches.%3Cp%3EWoori%20Mobile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSamsung's%20flagship%20models%20like%20the%20S23%20Ultra%20and%20S24%20Ultra%20offer%20exceptional%20camera%20and%20audio%20capabilities%2C%20especially%20in%20low%20light%20and%20concert%20environments%2C%20making%20them%20ideal%20for%20fans%20looking%20to%20record%20memories%20in%20high%20definition%2C%26quot%3B%20Han%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20company%20serves%2050%20to%20100%20rental%20customers%20a%20month%2C%20typically%20renting%20out%20the%20phones%20for%20three%20to%20seven%20days.%20They%20see%20a%20spike%20in%20activity%20during%20major%20K-pop%20festivals%20and%20tour%20seasons%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHan%20said%20Woori%20Mobile%20keeps%20an%20inventory%20of%20about%2020%20Samsung%20devices%2C%20but%20it%20plans%20to%20expand%20to%20other%20models%20like%20the%20Galaxy%20Z%20Fold%20and%20Flip%20series%20and%20add%20more%20mid-range%20models%20for%20budget-conscious%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForholiday%2C%20a%20luggage%20storage%20and%20rental%20company%20in%20Seoul%2C%20also%20offers%20phone%20rentals%2C%20with%20its%20services%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klook.com%2Factivity%2F126390-incheon-airport-galaxy-s-ultra-series-phone-rental%2F%3Fspm%3DActivity.TopNavigation.SelectCurrency%26clickId%3D0286cf42e5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavailable%20on%20Klook%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20has%20rented%20phones%20to%20more%20than%202%2C000%20customers%2C%20per%20the%20Klook%20listing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20rents%20the%20S23%20Ultra%20for%2011%2C800