t%3BLet's%20use%20AI%20and%20then%20let's%20build%20a%20product.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20problem%20could%20have%20been%20solved%20in%20other%20ways%2C%20what%20would%20it%20look%20like%3F%20And%20if%20they%20are%20using%20Gen%20AI%2C%20is%20AI%20the%20best%20use%20of%20technology%20in%20that%20case%3F%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20it%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20customer%20facing%20a%20problem%2C%20you%20really%20don't%20care%20how%20to%20solve%20it.%20It's%20more%20about%2C%20are%20you%20solving%20these%20problems%20for%20the%20customer%20in%20a%20better%20way%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounders%20usually%20start%20thinking%3A%20If%20somebody%20else%20is%20going%20to%20use%20the%20same%20idea%2C%20use%20AI%20or%20Gen%20AI%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20faster.%20Founders%20iterate%20a%20lot%20and%20keep%20trying%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20through%20different%20mechanisms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECan%20you%20be%20super%20laser-focused%20on%20the%20customer%3F%20Can%20you%20really%20identify%20how%20this%20technology%20can%20specifically%20solve%20the%20problem%3F%20If%20it%20doesn't%2C%20find%20other%20ways%20to%20solve%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272de6cc0-e841-4a31-81b2-2a2da616d30f%5C%22%3E2.%20Get%20product-market%20fit%20right%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20sometimes%20measure%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-every-founder-needs-to-know-about-market-fit-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproduct-market%20fit%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20incorrect%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%2C%20even%20before%20building%20the%20product%2C%20their%20product%20market%20fit%20is%20not%20very%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20about%20100%20or%2010%2C000%20people%20looking%20at%20this%20product%20and%20just%20being%20aware%20of%20it.%20Many%20times%2C%20the%20first-time%20sale%20is%20not%20a%20good%20mechanism%20because%20all%20of%20those%20metrics%20can%20be%20gamified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20m