ederal%20Reserve%20Chairman%20Jerome%20Powell%20is%20a%20graduate%20of%20Princeton%20University.%3Cp%3EBonnie%20Cash%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJerome%20Powell%20addressed%20graduates%20on%20Sunday%20at%20his%20alma%20mater%2C%20Princeton%20University.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPowell%20told%20the%20graduates%20he%20didn't%20major%20in%20economics%20in%20college%20because%20he%20found%20it%20%26quot%3Bboring.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20Princeton%2C%20Powell%20went%20to%20law%20school%20and%20decades%20later%20became%20chairman%20of%20the%20Federal%20Reserve.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20Reserve%20Chairman%20Jerome%20Powell%20told%20Princeton%20University%20graduates%20on%20Sunday%20that%20he%20didn't%20major%20in%20economics%20as%20a%20student%20because%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20found%20the%20subject%20%26quot%3Bboring%20and%20useless.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Powell%20gave%20the%20Baccalaureate%20address%20at%20Princeton%2C%20where%20he%20graduated%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20politics%2C%20he%20recounted%20his%20path%20to%20a%20career%20that%20included%20the%20private%20sector%20and%20government%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20real%20plan%20for%20life%20after%20Princeton%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMany%20of%20my%20classmates%20and%20friends%20went%20straight%20into%20prestigious%20graduate%20schools%2C%20politics%2C%20or%20Wall%20Street.%20Others%20went%20on%20to%20global%20capitals%2C%20the%20military%2C%20or%20the%20Peace%20Corps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20brushed%20off%20my%20parents'%20one%20academic%20suggestion%2C%20which%20was%20to%20major%20in%20economics%2C%20which%20struck%20me%20as%20boring%20and%20useless.%20After%2013%20years%20at%20the%20Fed%2C%20I%20admit%20I%20was%20wrong%20about%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowell%20then%20spoke%20about%20life%20after%20Princeton%20and%20how%20it%20set%20him%20up%20for%20h