to%20hear%20is%20that%20I%20hate%20her%20fianc%C3%A9.%20I%20think%20he's%20a%20nice%20enough%20guy%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20him%20I%20take%20issue%20with.%20It's%20how%20young%20they%20are.%20I've%20promised%20to%20give%20her%20%2410%2C000%20to%20help%20pay%20for%20her%20wedding%20for%20years%2C%20but%20now%20that%20feels%20like%20a%20high%20price%20for%20what%20I%20truly%20believe%20will%20be%20the%20worst%20mistake%20of%20her%20life.%20What%20should%20I%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Mom%20with%20Misgivings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Misgivings%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMistakes%20are%20tricky%20things.%20You%20regret%20marrying%20so%20young%2C%20but%20if%20Rumplestiltskin%20appeared%20on%20your%20doorstep%20and%20offered%20you%20a%20do-over%20that%20wiped%20your%20children%20from%20existence%2C%20my%20guess%20is%2C%20you'd%20turn%20him%20down%20flat.%20You%20and%20your%20ex%20would%20likely%20both%20undo%20his%20infidelity%20if%20you%20could%2C%20but%20then%20you'd%20still%20be%20trapped%20in%20an%20unhappy%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMistakes%20can%20range%20from%20Bob%20Ross's%20%26quot%3Bhappy%20little%20accidents%26quot%3B%20to%20devastating%20tragedies%2C%20but%20they%20all%20become%20part%20of%20our%20stories.%20They%20alter%20our%20lives%20and%20the%20lives%20of%20those%20around%20us.%20If%20we%20never%20made%20any%20mistakes%2C%20we%20would%20have%20less%20of%20everything%2C%20including%20the%20necessary%20experience%20to%20recognize%20and%20avoid%20future%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20parents%2C%20we%20want%20to%20do%20that%20part%20for%20our%20kids.%20We%20want%20to%20struggle%20through%20tough%20consequences%20so%20they%20never%20have%20to.%20Sometimes%20this%20works.%20Sometimes%20our%20cautionary%20tales%20and%20wise%20counsel%20get%20through%2C%20and%20our%20kids%20never%20have%20to%20experience%20the%20pain%20we%20endured.%20Other%20times%2C%20they%20have%20to%20make%20their%20own%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20children%20are%20living%20out%20their%20own%20stories%20full%20of%20twists%20and%20turns%2C%20magnificent%20triumphs%2C%20happy%20accidents%2C%20and%20yes%2C%20though%20as%20a%20mother%2C%20my%20stomach%20twists%20even%20writing%20this%2C%20devastating%20tragedies.%20Sometimes%20they%20will%20lose%2C%20sometimes%20they%20will%20win%2C%20but%20it%20was%20always%20their%20game%20to%20play.%20Not%20ours.%20We're%20the%20fans%20cheering%20on%20the%20sidelines.%20Our%20children%20deserve%20to%20live%20full%20lives%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bfull%26quot%3B%20includes%20even%20the%20hard%20parts%20of%20being%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20reminded%20of%20gymnast%20Aly%20Raisman's%20parents'%20viral%20behavior%20during%20the%202012%20Olympics.%20Up%20in%20the%20stands%2C%20they%20swayed%20and%20squirmed%20and%20winced%20with%20every%20step%20in%20their%20talented%20daughter's%20complex%20routine.%20I%20can%20only%20imagine%20the%20sacrifices%20they%20made%20to%20get%20Aly%20on%20that%20stage%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20London%20Olympics%2C%20among%20the%20elite%20of%20the%20elite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20they%20were%20a%20middle-aged%20couple%20sitting%20in%20stadium%20seats%20and%20wearing%20jeans%2C%20it%20seemed%20as%20if%2C%20as%20they%20watched%20their%20daughter%2C%20their%20consciousnesses%20left%20their%20bodies%20and%20joined%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20launched%20her%20body%20over%20the%20vault%2C%20they%20leaned%20back%20in%20their%20seats%2C%20eyes%20full%20of%20profound%20empathy%2C%20and%20still%2C%20Aly%20alone%20flew%20through%20the%20air%20and%20stuck%20her%20landing.%20Not%20her%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20truest%2C%20hardest%20part%20of%20parenting%20%E2%80%94%20letting%20go.%20Remembering%20that%20our%20kids'%20lives%20belong%20to%20them%2C%20not%20us.%20This%20includes%20their%20successes%2C%20failures%2C%20joy%2C%20and%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20give%20your%20daughter%20your%20blessing%20in%20the%20form%20of%20%2410%2C000%2C%20or%20not.%20Your%20daughter%20might%20heed%20your%20protests%2C%20or%20not.%20And%20still%2C%20this%20is%20her%20life%20and%20her%20mistake%20to%20make.%20She%20could%20marry%20this%20young%20man%20in%20a%20year%2C%20repeat%20your%20mistakes%2C%20and%20bear%20the%20same%20heartbreaking%20consequences.%20Or%2C%20she%20could%20take%20your%20advice%2C%20tell%20him%20she%20wants%20to%20wait%2C%20break%20up%2C%20and%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20her%20life%20wondering%20what%20could%20have%20been%20if%20she%20had%20just%20followed%20her%2020-year-old%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20why%2C%20as%20parents%2C%20we%20must%20distinguish%20between%20our%20empathy%20for%20our%20children%20%E2%80%94%20that%20crackling%20swirl%20of%20adoration%2C%20devotion%2C%20and%20personal%20investment%20%E2%80%94%20and%20their%20lived%20experiences.%20We%20want%20the%20best%20for%20them%2C%20so%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20feel%20certain%20things%2C%20but%20they're%20the%20ones%20who%20will%20feel%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20promised%20your%20daughter%20that%20when%20she%20found%20the%20person%20she%20wanted%20to%20marry%2C%20you%20would%20give%20her%20%2410%2C000%20to%20do%20it.%20Keep%20your%20word.%20You've%20given%20her%20your%20best%20advice%20and%20told%20her%20what%20you%20would%20do%20if%20it%20were%20your%20life.%20Now%20show%20her%20that%20you%20will%20have%20her%20back%20regardless.%20If%20your%20misgivings%20are%20confirmed%2C%20she%20will%20know%20she%20can%20count%20on%20you.%20If%20you're%20wrong%20and%20she%20goes%20on%20to%20have%20a%20storybook%20happily%20ever%20after%2C%20she%20will%20remember%20you%20believed%20in%20her%2C%20even%20when%20you%20didn't%20approve%20of%20her%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20support%20doesn't%20have%20to%20look%20like%20just%20hopes%2C%20prayers%2C%20and%20a%20shoulder%20to%20cry%20on%2C%20either.%20You%20can%20start%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com