0return%20to%20meaningful%20life%20roles.%20Many%20individuals%20live%20independently%2C%20maintain%20jobs%2C%20and%20have%20fulfilling%20relationships.%20The%20earlier%20the%20intervention%2C%20the%20better%20the%20outcome.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMyth%204%3A%20%E2%80%9CMedicines%20alone%20can%20fix%20it%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20medication%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20reducing%20symptoms%2C%20schizophrenia%20is%20not%20just%20a%20medical%20issue%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20bio-psycho-social%20condition%2C%20says%20Dr.%20Khanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBiologically%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20chemical%20imbalance%20in%20the%20brain.%20Psychologically%2C%20factors%20like%20childhood%20trauma%20or%20poor%20coping%20mechanisms%20contribute.%20And%20socially%2C%20how%20families%20and%20communities%20treat%20the%20person%20plays%20a%20huge%20role.%E2%80%9D%20This%20means%20recovery%20needs%20more%20than%20pills.%20It%20needs%20psychotherapy%2C%20social%20support%2C%20family%20involvement%2C%20and%20community%20acceptance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%E2%80%99t%20just%20give%20someone%20medicine%20and%20leave%20them%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20rest.%20Healing%20is%20a%20holistic%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-27_11zon-1748009141.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sharma%20points%20out%20that%20in%20genetically%20vulnerable%20individuals%2C%20trauma%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20trigger%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-27_11zon-1748009141.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-27_11zon-1748009141-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-