0for%20holistic%2C%20person-centred%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recovery%20often%20involves%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Medication%20(primarily%20antipsychotics)%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Psychotherapy%20(especially%20CBT%20for%20psychosis)%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Social%20skills%20training%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Family%20support%20and%20psychoeducation%2C%20and%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Rehabilitation%20services%20(vocational%20and%20community%20support).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMyth%205%3A%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99ll%20never%20get%20better%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20belief%20can%20be%20especially%20harmful%2C%20and%20simply%20isn%E2%80%99t%20true.%20While%20schizophrenia%20is%20a%20chronic%20condition%2C%20many%20people%20improve%20significantly%20over%20time%20with%20the%20right%20combination%20of%20care%20and%20support.%20Some%20achieve%20what%20doctors%20call%20%E2%80%9Cfunctional%20recovery%E2%80%9D%2C%20where%20they%20can%20manage%20symptoms%20and%20live%20full%2C%20independent%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wish%20more%20people%20understood%20that%20schizophrenia%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20end%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr.%20Khanna.%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20long%20journey.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20journey%20people%20can%20walk%20and%20thrive%20through%2C%20if%20they%E2%80%99re%20supported.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Sharma%20echoes%20this%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20society%20understands%20that%20schizophrenia%20is%20not%20about%20demons%20or%20split%20minds%2C%20but%20a%20treatable%20condition%2C%20we%20can%20build%20systems%20that%20offer%20real%20hope.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChanging%20the%20way%20we%20see%20schizophrenia%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20danger%20of%20misinformation%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20confusion%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20neglect%2C%20discrimination%2C%20and%20delayed%20care.%20Across%20India%2C%20an%20estimated%203%20in%20every%201%2C000%20people%20live%20with%20schizophrenia%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Mental%20Health%20Survey%20(2015%E2%80%9316).%20That%E2%80%99s%20over%204%20million%20people%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20never%20receive%20a%20formal%20diagnosis%20or%20access%20to%20consistent%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20availability%20of%20treatment%20options%2C%20nearly%2075%25%20of%20people%20with%20severe%20mental%20disorders%20in%20India%2C%20including%20schizophrenia%2C%20do%20not%20receive%20any%20mental%20health%20care%2C%20as%20highlighted%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO).%20Often%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20illness%20itself%20but%20the%20fear%2C%20silence%2C%20and%20stigma%20surrounding%20it%20that%20keep%20people%20from%20reaching%20out%20for%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-28_11zon-1748009317.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20While%20schizophrenia%20is%20a%20chronic%20condition%2C%20many%20people%20improve%20significantly%20over%20time%20with%20the%20right%20combination%20of%20care%20and%20support.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-28_11zon-1748009317.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-28_11zon-1748009317-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-28_11zon-1748009317-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-28_11zon-1748009317-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-28_11zon-1748009317-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-437830