D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20moment%2C%20I%20stood%20still%2C%20silenced%20by%20the%20scale%20of%20it%20all.%20I%20had%20come%20to%20Ranthambore%20looking%20for%20something%20wild.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20it%20would%20begin%20with%20stone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETrinetra%20Ganesh%20Temple%3A%20Devotion%20carved%20in%20stone%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigh%20atop%20the%20fort%2C%20nestled%20within%20a%20quiet%20courtyard%2C%20we%20reached%20the%20%3Cstrong%3ETrinetra%20Ganesh%20Temple%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20small%20shrine%20that%20exuded%20an%20almost%20tangible%20aura%20of%20faith.%20I%20had%20heard%20whispers%20of%20its%20legend%20even%20before%20I%20began%20the%20climb%3A%20that%20during%20a%20siege%20in%201299%20by%20Alauddin%20Khilji%E2%80%99s%20forces%2C%20King%20Hammir%20Dev%20Chauhan%2C%20a%20devout%20follower%20of%20Lord%20Ganesh%2C%20had%20a%20dream.%20In%20it%2C%20Ganesh%20promised%20that%20his%20troubles%20would%20be%20over%20by%20dawn.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20a%20self-manifested%20idol%20of%20Ganesh%20with%20three%20eyes%20(Trinetra)%20was%20discovered%20within%20the%20fort.%20Soon%20after%2C%20the%20siege%20inexplicably%20lifted.%20The%20idol%20remained%2C%20and%20so%20did%20the%20belief.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20sanctum%2C%20the%20air%20felt%20cool%20and%20still.%20The%20Trinetra%20idol%2C%20flanked%20by%20his%20consorts%20Riddhi%20and%20Siddhi%20and%20sons%20Shubh%20and%20Labh%2C%20exuded%20a%20quiet%20serenity.%20It%20is%20said%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20few%20temples%20in%20the%20world%20that%20depicts%20Lord%20Ganesh%20in%20this%20complete%20familial%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebette