icated%20postbox%20for%20Lord%20Ganesh.%E2%80%9D%20He%20smiled%20and%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20yes%2C%20the%20postman%20does%20deliver%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20something%20profoundly%20moving%20about%20that.%20In%20a%20world%20of%20fleeting%20rituals%2C%20here%20was%20a%20practice%20rooted%20in%20belief%2C%20blessing%2C%20and%20the%20quiet%20hope%20that%20beginnings%20like%20marriages%20deserve%20divine%20acknowledgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStanding%20there%2C%20I%20thought%20the%20rugged%20stone%20walls%20of%20the%20fort%2C%20which%20had%20once%20echoed%20with%20the%20cries%20of%20war%20and%20conquest%2C%20now%20stood%20silent%20witness%20to%20centuries%20of%20devotion.%20It%20struck%20me%20then%20that%20Ranthambore%20Fort%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F401836%2Findian-currency-money-features-indian-monuments-konark-temple-hampi-chariot%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistorical%20monument%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20a%20breathing%2C%20believing%20space.%20A%20place%20where%20faith%20had%20outlasted%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20place%20that%20stays%20with%20you%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20descended%20from%20the%20fort%2C%20the%20jungle%20began%20to%20rise%20again%20in%20the%20distance.%20But%20something%20had%20shifted.%20I%20had%20come%20to%20Ranthambore%20hoping%20to%20lock%20eyes%20with%20a%20tiger%2C%20to%20chase%20that%20fleeting%20thrill%20of%20the%20wild%2C%20which%20I%20did%20during%20my%20safari.%20And%20yet%2C%20it%20was%20the%20fort%2C%20not%20the%20forest%2C%20that%20had%20captured%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FView-from-the-fort_11zon-1748149622.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22120