ng%20to%20make%20the%20%E2%80%98Soak%20It%20Up%E2%80%99%20moisturiser%20and%20soaps%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20I%20can%20make%20deodorants%2C%20lip%20balms%2C%20and%20shampoo%20bars%2C%20and%20I%20even%20train%20others.%20It%20has%20been%20such%20a%20beautiful%20journey.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20reflects%20on%20how%20the%20company%20has%20shifted%20her%20values.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20learnt%20so%20much%20about%20sustainability%2C%20and%20I%20never%20waste%20food%20or%20water%20now.%20I%20see%20every%20resource%20as%20precious.%20Bare%20Necessities%20taught%20me%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20that%2C%20it%20gave%20her%20community.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20women%20here%20are%20amazing.%20Everyone%E2%80%99s%20so%20grounded%20and%20compassionate.%20It%20helped%20me%20see%20that%20I%20am%20not%20alone%20in%20my%20struggles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T114359.784_11zon-1747894453.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20production%20and%20warehouse%20team%20of%20the%20startup%20is%20100%25%20women-run%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T114359.784_11zon-1747894453.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T114359.784_11zon-1747894453-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T114359.784_11zon-1747894453-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T114359.784_11zon-1747894453-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-22T114359.784_11zon-1747894453-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-436582%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20production%20and%20warehouse%20team%20of%20the%20startup%20is%20100%25%20women-run%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20for%20Veena%20Suryanarayan%2C%20joining%20the%20company%20marked%20more%20than%20just%20the%20start%20of%20a%20career%2C%20it%20helped%20to%20shift%20her%20perspective.%20She%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20born%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20raised%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20which%20I%20now%20call%20home.%E2%80%9D%20With%20a%20background%20in%20political%20science%2C%20journalism%2C%20and%20economics%2C%20she%20had%20long%20been%20interested%20in%20how%20systems%20and%20stories%20shape%20the%20world.%20When%20she%20spotted%20a%20job%20posting%20for%20a%20Communication%20Executive%20at%20Bare%20Necessities%2C%20she%20did%20not%20think%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20my%20first%20job%2C%20and%20I%20could%20not%20have%20asked%20for%20a%20better%20place%20to%20begin.%20It%20gave%20me%20financial%20stability%20and%20purpose%2C%20something%20I%20value%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20Now%20Brand%20Marketing%20and%20Communications%20Supervisor%2C%20her%20role%20spans%20everything%20from%20customer%20relations%20and%20content%20creation%20to%20managing%20press%20and%20impact%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20in%20a%20small%20and%20dynamic%20team%2C%20she%20has%20embraced%20the%20chance%20to%20grow.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20led%20workshops%20for%20our%20women%E2%80%99s%20team%20on%20savings%20and%20financial%20discipline.%20It%20felt%20empowering%20to%20share%20what%20I%20have%20learnt%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp